<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #374151;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background: white;
        padding: 40px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #10b981;
        color: white;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .step-box {
        background: #d1fae5;
        border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      }
      .info-box {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .compliance-requirements {
        background: #fef3c7;
        border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      }
      .compliance-requirements ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .compliance-requirements li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“‹ Compliance Setup Required</h1>
      <p>Complete your compliance requirements to continue</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="step-box">
        <h2>Next Step: Compliance Setup</h2>
        <p>Great! Your billing setup for <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong> has been completed. Now it's time to complete the compliance requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Organization Progress</h3>
        <p><strong>Organization:</strong> <%= @organization.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Current Status:</strong> <%= @organization.activation_status.humanize %></p>
        <p><strong>Next Step:</strong> Compliance Setup</p>
      </div>

      <div class="compliance-requirements">
        <h3>Compliance Requirements</h3>
        <p>To complete this step, you'll need to provide:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Business registration documents</li>
          <li>Tax identification information</li>
          <li>Compliance policy acknowledgments</li>
          <li>Any other required regulatory documentation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Ready to complete your compliance setup? Continue with this step now:</p>
      
      <a href="<%= tenant_activation_compliance_url %>" class="button">Complete Compliance Setup</a>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about compliance requirements or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from HBS Data Processing System.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
